<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <!-- Include Bootstrap CSS (either hosted or local) -->
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<style>
    /* Custom CSS for spacing */
    .form-check-inline {
        margin-right: 50px; /* Adjust the spacing as needed */
    }
</style>
<body>
 <h1 class="mt-1 text-center">Which tennis player are you?</h1>
<div class="container  d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center" >

    <form method="post" action="/test">
        <p>Whats more important to you, trophies or talent? (1 talent - 3 trophies)</p>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="form-check form-switch form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" id="inlineRadio1" name="talent" value="option1">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="inlineRadio1">1</label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" id="inlineRadio2" name="talent" value="option2">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="inlineRadio2">2</label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" id="inlineRadio3" name="talent" value="option3">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="inlineRadio3">3</label>
            </div>
            
        </div>
        <p>Do you prefer aggressive or defensive gameplay?</p>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="form-check form-switch form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" id="inlineRadio1" name="gameplay" value="option1">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="inlineRadio1">1</label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" id="inlineRadio2" name="gameplay" value="option2">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="inlineRadio2">2</label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" id="inlineRadio3" name="gameplay" value="option3">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="inlineRadio3">3</label>
            </div>

        </div>
        <p>Which tennis surface do you enjoy playing on the most? (Grass, clay, hard court, or indoor)</p>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="form-check form-switch form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" id="inlineRadio1" name="surface" value="option1">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="inlineRadio1">1</label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" id="inlineRadio2" name="surface" value="option2">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="inlineRadio2">2</label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch form-check-inline">
                <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" id="inlineRadio3" name="surface" value="option3">
                <label class="form-check-label" for="inlineRadio3">3</label>
            </div>

        </div>
        <input type="submit" class="btn mt-2 btn-primary" value="Send">
        <!-- You can add more radio buttons or other form elements here -->
    </form>
</div>

<!-- Include Bootstrap JavaScript (optional, required for certain components) -->
<!-- Place it at the end of the body to improve page loading performance -->
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
